WEBVTT

1
00:19:07.360 --> 00:19:08.460 
我等不起了
I've already been away too long.

2
00:19:08.530 --> 00:19:10.500 
给个机会吧
Just give me a shot.

3
00:19:10.820 --> 00:19:12.360 
等等 等等
Whoa. Hold it.

4
00:19:14.240 --> 00:19:15.830 
好吧 如果您对我没什么兴趣
Well, if you're not interested in me,

5
00:19:15.870 --> 00:19:18.770 
那中尉应该会对你非常感兴趣
I think the lieutenant might be very interested in you.

6
00:19:22.430 --> 00:19:23.910 
威胁我
Blackmail.

7
00:19:26.140 --> 00:19:27.080 
中尉
Lieutenant.

8
00:19:27.160 --> 00:19:28.030 
上尉
Captain.

9
00:19:29.120 --> 00:19:31.710 
中尉 我们逮捕了一名逃兵
Lieutenant, we have apprehended a deserter.

10
00:19:31.780 --> 00:19:32.710 
把他带走
Take him.

11
00:19:32.770 --> 00:19:33.520 
我说 等一下
Wait.

12
00:19:33.600 --> 00:19:36.460 
我就知道 你小子不是个好东西
I should've known. This one's a troublemaker.

13
00:19:36.520 --> 00:19:38.700 
他还是个骗子 他说的话可别信
And a liar. Don't believe anything he says.

